3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with deep learning networks and their application to face recognition. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with image-based tasks. 
5. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a possible category as the paper deals with deep neural networks.
